<h1>VendorSweets New!</h1>
<p>Find me in app/views/vendor_sweets/create.html.erb</p>



choose a Vendor from a select dropdown
choose a Sweet from a select dropdown
enter a price
submit the form to create a VendorSweet
Once the VendorSweet is created, the user should be redirected 
to the selected vendor's show page.

<%= form_for (@vendor_sweets) do |f| %>
 
  <%= f.label :price%>
  <%= f.number_field :price%>

  <%= f.label :vendor %>
  <%= f.collection_select :vendor_id, Vendor.all, :id, :name %>

  <%= f.label :sweet %>
  <%= f.collection_select :sweet_id, Sweet.all, :id, :name %>

  <%= f.submit %>
  <%end%>